{"title":"阿里妈妈 | 吉祥物AI视觉设计升级","slug":"yhnuqzgife6z5la2","summary":"原文链接： https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/L3fWaqRikeHNsfxec6_9CA 升级背景 在数字化时代，品牌形象的塑造愈发重要。阿里妈妈作为阿里巴巴集团旗下的营销广告平台，致力于为商家提供高效的广告投放和数据分析服务。 为了更好地传达品牌的核心价值","category":"2. 国内产品","tags":["PART6️⃣ AI产品设计案例分析库","2. 国内产品"],"featured":false,"order":102,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2025-08-04","wordCount":2354,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/yhnuqzgife6z5la2","html":"<blockquote data-lake-id=\"u7abff74e\" id=\"u7abff74e\"><p data-lake-id=\"ud01c10b9\" id=\"ud01c10b9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u26e61334\" id=\"u26e61334\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">原文链接：</span><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/L3fWaqRikeHNsfxec6_9CA\" data-lake-id=\"u6127c5dc\" id=\"u6127c5dc\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf0950683\" id=\"uf0950683\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/L3fWaqRikeHNsfxec6_9CA</span></a></p></blockquote><h1 data-lake-id=\"iTXgz\" id=\"iTXgz\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0c1987a6\" id=\"u0c1987a6\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">升级背景</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u39d1b73e\" id=\"u39d1b73e\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf5363955\" id=\"uf5363955\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在数字化时代，品牌形象的塑造愈发重要。阿里妈妈作为阿里巴巴集团旗下的营销广告平台，致力于为商家提供高效的广告投放和数据分析服务。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2306cb21\" id=\"u2306cb21\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426211220-23aa6322-52b8-4a26-ab6f-8b6e34c7b7d2.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ua824bfd1-0ded-474c-bd0e-02506be3b40%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23414f52%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u21bc9ae4%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uba1546e8\" id=\"uba1546e8\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u83780e8f\" id=\"u83780e8f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">为了更好地传达品牌的核心价值观，阿里妈妈吉祥物选择袋鼠作为其基础的形象来由，他象征着关怀、亲和与成长，正如阿里妈妈希望通过其服务帮助商家实现更好的经营效果。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue611b0db\" id=\"ue611b0db\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426211217-1c921679-3d13-4cee-9524-ddea917e1b3d.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u458ba0fe-2328-4bd2-9fc3-c95b371c2a8%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%234144fd%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ue6a7252a%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uf6c1422d\" id=\"uf6c1422d\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue861686f\" id=\"ue861686f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">从业务需求出发袋耳朵用讨喜的人物化形象来象征品牌内涵以唤起受众对品牌的注意和好感，从而影响客户决策，为品牌带来价值。袋耳朵全新亮相，作为toB业务的柔性传播代言人，强化妈妈品牌形象和感知力。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1a0d46c2\" id=\"u1a0d46c2\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2abeae99\" id=\"u2abeae99\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">通过拓展全新的触点、创意玩法和品牌co-branding持续扩大袋耳朵内外部的影响力和认知。</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"QpPJ4\" id=\"QpPJ4\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub408cd40\" id=\"ub408cd40\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">形象设定与优化</span></h1><h2 data-lake-id=\"xHzyj\" id=\"xHzyj\"><span data-lake-id=\"u792ba878\" id=\"u792ba878\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1. 形象转变</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u31166ab8\" id=\"u31166ab8\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u37571181\" id=\"u37571181\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在此次升级中的核心诉求是袋耳朵数智化转型，从袋耳朵1.0到如今的3.0，袋耳朵从最早期的橘色到品牌蓝色的继承，从还原袋鼠本身形态特征到现在更加显化的继承阿里妈妈科技的数智营销的基因。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4ee98fcd\" id=\"u4ee98fcd\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1fa15fba\" id=\"u1fa15fba\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在外形上比融入了更多品牌图形的特色，如耳朵造型、脸型的正圆优化，尾巴的纯圆造型，及整体身体的柔和处理。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4186d0a8\" id=\"u4186d0a8\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1746426211213-dbb3628f-7404-4aa4-9193-054d633c82cd.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u3f5c698f-bf3d-46b7-8ebe-0daddddb5c0%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1079%2C%22originHeight%22%3A607%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%232451f0%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u79ae25fd%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ueaa413a5\" id=\"ueaa413a5\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426211173-5339d981-03da-4246-8d8e-191f86cf1cf4.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u0fe86843-f7ef-4e61-9fea-73cf856705e%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23efefef%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u8ec6dd9e%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u479f7d1c\" id=\"u479f7d1c\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426211315-022a821e-8d09-4789-91cf-3f76bbf20d6a.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u6a72423d-f1ce-4bf6-ac2d-c8930b1316b%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2390ebf7%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ue40bc4a3%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"EL2Mz\" id=\"EL2Mz\"><span data-lake-id=\"u191a9728\" id=\"u191a9728\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2. 记忆点-数智袋+数智皮肤</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u7cece1b5\" id=\"u7cece1b5\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf56e0808\" id=\"uf56e0808\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">外形上袋鼠最特别的“袋子”的特征，经历了从传统的物理化袋子特征向数智化的转变，原先的袋子特征过于强调物理形态，而新的设计将袋子变成了一个虚拟态，能够展示多种元素，增强了其作为品牌超级容器的功能，能实时展示阿里妈妈的各种服务和产品信息。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7740cee4\" id=\"u7740cee4\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4a0f3b9b\" id=\"u4a0f3b9b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">同时袋鼠的皮肤也是基于AI基因呈现出多元百变的状态，伴随着心情、场景、内容的表达瞬息万变。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u12a39522\" id=\"u12a39522\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426211633-0a2f4a31-f3cf-453e-9fae-991277514edf.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u8b0bfdc5-25b3-4d27-b718-9e3ceded270%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A429%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2369daf6%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ufb4760d2%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7e529cda\" id=\"u7e529cda\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1746426211593-f7310bde-f6d4-4ff8-ad61-6d1707bc295a.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u6a613e5d-2c86-46e1-989f-df5e89cda21%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A338%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%234566a4%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u01b339d3%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue2ae7cb2\" id=\"ue2ae7cb2\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1746426211647-5011c9d6-4187-48ee-959e-b8010a07047f.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub00a5e8b-f833-47bd-bae8-8c4664cab34%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A800%2C%22originHeight%22%3A450%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2368b3d6%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u1b3eb662%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"ekHAW\" id=\"ekHAW\"><span data-lake-id=\"u90414b96\" id=\"u90414b96\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">3. 更为拟人化</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uc79304cf\" id=\"uc79304cf\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u42ce16fe\" id=\"u42ce16fe\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">为了增强用户的亲和感，袋耳朵的外形进行了拟人化的优化。四肢从原先的动物形态转变为更接近人类的形态，这样不仅方便了用户的互动体验，也使得袋耳朵的形象更加友好，增强了品牌的IP感。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u0f4e442e\" id=\"u0f4e442e\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3c4a4657\" id=\"u3c4a4657\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在其动作表现及服饰穿搭上给到了更多发挥的空间。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u0e58cbcf\" id=\"u0e58cbcf\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426211711-17431ad9-7911-4ccc-bbeb-1905fab90714.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc13c42a4-d6e7-4a9a-9092-9d9966ed072%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%2