e%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23c1c3c2%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u03dfff9d%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u91ec0dec\" id=\"u91ec0dec\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426213383-c42378f0-9afb-4df6-b98d-ca4cba2cf4c6.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ue471122a-012b-41f9-bb08-b9787009923%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A3248%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2379c69b%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u8c1fdc0d%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4aea0dae\" id=\"u4aea0dae\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u377a04a9\" id=\"u377a04a9\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">​</span><br></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"f4uQ2\" id=\"f4uQ2\"><span data-lake-id=\"u447894be\" id=\"u447894be\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">职能与世界</span></h1><h2 data-lake-id=\"htKjP\" id=\"htKjP\"><span data-lake-id=\"u70321557\" id=\"u70321557\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1. 能力</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u7667137f\" id=\"u7667137f\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9c86136d\" id=\"u9c86136d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">袋耳朵不仅是一个可爱的吉祥物，更是一个智能化的助手。袋耳朵被赋予了乐观、聪慧和乐于助人的性格。这些特质使得它在与用户的互动中，它能够倾听客户的需求，搜集信息，并在此基础上进行产品的研发与创新。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uac7d8bb8\" id=\"uac7d8bb8\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u42235ccb\" id=\"u42235ccb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">袋耳朵的智能化能力使得它能够实时分析市场数据，同时袋鼠的数智袋的能力着重于孵化AI、创新、营销产品，帮助商家制定更有效的营销策略。</span><span data-lake-id=\"u3d289550\" id=\"u3d289550\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">​</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9e253be7\" id=\"u9e253be7\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1746426213729-b108b00c-a300-4ea8-8df1-a036f911364a.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u3f8fa14f-c60e-4b64-aa45-8fb269bb56d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A338%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23c29fdc%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u44499106%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u910ec443\" id=\"u910ec443\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"udd143d6d\" id=\"udd143d6d\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在与行业合作方面，袋耳朵积极参与到不同的行业岛屿的开发中。这些行业岛屿是阿里妈妈与各行业合作伙伴共同打造的生态系统，袋耳朵作为其中的引导者，能更好的去和行业、生态、商家建联。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue9547d18\" id=\"ue9547d18\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1746426214865-10dbf1b7-086b-4c12-9e6b-9834e17c8cc5.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u020c8c79-bea8-4961-936f-c50a99f4420%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A338%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23749fbc%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uc56269f5%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc70d7f8e\" id=\"uc70d7f8e\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u97daea41\" id=\"u97daea41\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136)\">以AI之力 不断创造经营场景</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"gAnoz\" id=\"gAnoz\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7b119c5e\" id=\"u7b119c5e\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2. 数智世界的构建</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uc8e12a36\" id=\"uc8e12a36\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf94ac53e\" id=\"uf94ac53e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在新的品牌片中，袋耳朵被描绘为一个在数智世界中探索智慧体。他的数智世界是一个充满可能性的空间，袋耳朵在其中不断探索、发现和成长。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u18ebd42c\" id=\"u18ebd42c\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1746426214930-c1590fed-fc0e-49ce-8e6f-f444a947a33d.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22udc298db2-5676-487e-a71c-ba0adcf275f%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A338%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%238a77b0%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u7ac40380%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u545ac76b\" id=\"u545ac76b\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9c4aea1f\" id=\"u9c4aea1f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在这个世界中，袋耳朵不仅是一个信息的接收者，更是一个信息的传播者。它通过与用户的互动，将用户的需求转化为产品的创新，它不仅倾听客户的声音，并投入在产品的研发中，展现他在数字营销领域的前瞻性与创新性。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uba3cf7a9\" id=\"uba3cf7a9\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1746426219519-ca265511-d688-473d-ae53-71c0e04c2a90.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u388f5c5e-705f-4787-8ad9-56ed0d27d0b%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A338%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%239969b8%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u0c9a5d38%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u73d7c552\" id=\"u73d7c552\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub6c3026b\" id=\"ub6c3026b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136)\">以AI之力 不断理解数据</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4b3cae93\" id=\"u4b3cae93\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1746426228444-32b53110-065a-445a-bfb9-b71feade3f19.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u5261cf63-92aa-4739-94ba-12cdfff5499%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A600%2C%22originHeight%22%3A338%2C%22ratio%22%3A2