d=\"u802333bb\" id=\"u802333bb\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">全面的资产</span></h1><h2 data-lake-id=\"Wys1B\" id=\"Wys1B\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3faec88e\" id=\"u3faec88e\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">1.袋耳朵全新周边计划：</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u9c20761e\" id=\"u9c20761e\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud0e512c9\" id=\"ud0e512c9\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">首先，全新的3.0公仔首发焕新，推出基础版及限定镭射版2款公仔产品，周边部分基于workhard｜playhard推出2大系列，「袋」你一起从打工到生活，以节庆节点在甜蜜的春日带来了包包、配饰包挂、户外露营系列、餐具系列。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u8c82641f\" id=\"u8c82641f\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426246384-32745962-431d-4fb4-a6b5-bb4cd2438a69.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u2c00373a-8e8e-4ea2-b11c-8137c632318%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23ced4cd%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u4cc66f01%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9d5c54a0\" id=\"u9d5c54a0\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426247113-2cb11ec5-4cc0-415b-a7bc-c40e346ef27a.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ua2286a49-3dd9-408c-afa6-7f75351ecef%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A2123%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2324acd7%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u3bc9defc%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1ae58658\" id=\"u1ae58658\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u42ba976a\" id=\"u42ba976a\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">​</span><br></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"bb0dy\" id=\"bb0dy\"><span data-lake-id=\"uab14e04e\" id=\"uab14e04e\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">2.袋耳朵AI资产</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u7684097b\" id=\"u7684097b\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u71d7d526\" id=\"u71d7d526\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">区别于常规3D建模生产流程，这次运用IP Lora的生成能力，既可大大降低设计成本，也能在时间紧、角色多、任务重的背景下高效完成创意产出。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2287715e\" id=\"u2287715e\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub793207e\" id=\"ub793207e\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">品牌识别性：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ubba9db49\" id=\"ubba9db49\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">基于明确的设定规范。圆形的头部特征，圆形的耳朵，肚子的识别形，字母m光标的正确。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5848fc95\" id=\"u5848fc95\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6824f34c\" id=\"u6824f34c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">IP 一致性：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9783981f\" id=\"u9783981f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">材质、比例大小的一致性，确保整体视觉的高度统一。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ufaab52f1\" id=\"ufaab52f1\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua078ddbf\" id=\"ua078ddbf\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">丰富拓展性：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"udadbf1db\" id=\"udadbf1db\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">需要满足不同场景不同设定下的形象都保持良好稳定的输出效果，这样需要Lora模型有较强的泛化能力。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4c559328\" id=\"u4c559328\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc30f9b8f\" id=\"uc30f9b8f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">整个“炼丹”过程一共分为四部分：第一步-搜集素材，训练素材库非常重要，这一步就可使Lora在源头上保证质量。除去描写，在打标过程中，将打标的标注格式统一，根据不同类型增加画面关键词，才能更好地控制IP的产出；</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u04f51c98\" id=\"u04f51c98\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5b13c519\" id=\"u5b13c519\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">第二步-训练，将炼好的Lora模型进行批量生图，进行多维对比，检查稳定性、泛化性是否都达标；第三步-验收测试，进行不同描述词生图及叠加各风格lora，来看出图在服饰及复杂场景下的应用性。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u4b1489c0\" id=\"u4b1489c0\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426248351-19338fe6-4dbb-46bf-b075-cbf1aad1dffa.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ue2f9cb4a-7b1d-409a-a474-cdb69d58341%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A514%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23484bd7%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uafaef7ac%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ucf19c004\" id=\"ucf19c004\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426249627-1c5a2f79-881d-4f1d-acaf-4c6189ecd4c1.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ud404d596-d8cc-4186-9ada-84900ef5a7f%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1687%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23b5bd87%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u4f463016%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"Eklv4\" id=\"Eklv4\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf49adff5\" id=\"uf49adff5\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">3.在创新互动中的应用</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u30a2d3a8\" id=\"u30a2d3a8\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf673201c\" id=\"uf673201c\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在阿里妈妈的商家会议场合打造定制抽卡互动，当中所有的数字福卡的制作都基于AI生产完成。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud32fa8b9\" id=\"ud32fa8b9\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc136949b\" id=\"uc136949b\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">以袋耳朵作为召集人开启阿里妈妈未来商业奖全新升级和未来品牌共建启动仪式，并引入AR能力定制福卡，为品牌送上经营祝福，通过与用户的互动，袋耳朵能够更好地传达品牌的价值观和服务理念。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u37e02874\" id=\"u37e02874\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426250669-3fd3c005-3a8a-46fa-840f-369e21a0dbaf.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u0da81bfb-7ceb-4ed0-a7e0-36eda939380%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A714%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%233d4d5a%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u75481f98%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua5c2e5f0\" id=\"ua5c2e5f0\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426252191-e57ed427-d3b9-4f1e-8250-0e12bb190839.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u90c39ae0-378c-4cb2-8518-3f69d879078%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1000%2C%22originHeight%22%3A537%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23121439%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u4131632c%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue19691e0\" id=\"ue19691e0\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426252131-fde1439d-0276-496b-99e2-ca73884606d0.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u16c13b84-bab3-4d76-a073-d77f9e59b3e%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A653%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%232e334d%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u914d1b9b%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc9840fe2\" id=\"uc9840fe2\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426253248-9932f640-28e5-428c-ad9e-1e5849630ce4.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc1012378-7f89-430b-8803-46439abfb7d%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1687%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2337435a%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ufae373fd%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3ba6abc5\" id=\"u3ba6abc5\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u22e9b781\" id=\"u22e9b781\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136)\">AI定制30款赢新福卡</span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"zRswk\" id=\"zRswk\"><span data-lake-id=\"u34b36306\" id=\"u34b36306\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">传播｜影响力</span></h1><h2 data-lake-id=\"enaMO\" id=\"enaMO\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf2f10588\" id=\"uf2f10588\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">对客亮相</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uc7a79703\" id=\"uc7a79703\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uba364264\" id=\"uba364264\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">在近期的阿里妈妈峰会中，袋耳朵也有着重要的亮相。打造线下巨型拍照装置，抢占嘉宾视觉注意力；在拍照展区以袋耳朵的肚子作为交互道具，加强与嘉宾之间的互动。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua35848ac\" id=\"ua35848ac\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1746426253442-ae7eda69-2113-4bac-a2a4-230a072ce70f.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u9829079f-649c-47d9-a325-da71bcafb7f%22%2C%22clie