image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1746426255178-62b99101-9ce9-4f34-b5fb-12425df8a729.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ue37d2c07-9304-4b0c-8b5c-d8c8eaa9ae3%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A800%2C%22originHeight%22%3A477%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23346e7d%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u44325d66%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u986e14b1\" id=\"u986e14b1\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u818ca83f\" id=\"u818ca83f\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136)\">AIGC创意预热</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u84cc0a3c\" id=\"u84cc0a3c\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9c190ef5\" id=\"u9c190ef5\" class=\"lake-fontsize-1515\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">以袋耳朵担任数字经营官在商家会议参与产品发布、奖项颁布等核心环节，在传递业务策略的同时表达IP与业务的紧密关联度，客户在接触到袋耳朵时，能够迅速联想到阿里妈妈的服务与价值，从而增强了品牌的记忆点。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1f0a1da4\" id=\"u1f0a1da4\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2025%2Fgif%2F1206632%2F1746426255496-199a726e-4c5f-4be1-b57b-447d60f4bb93.gif%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22uc1f5a9ec-18a4-4954-b7a5-24fda33c66a%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uddc26f9f-6ab4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A700%2C%22originHeight%22%3A131%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C